ABOUT

Magic Month Club is a delightful picture book and activity series that brings the months of the year to life for young readers. Each book in the series celebrates a different month, highlighting what makes it unique—from seasonal joys and holidays to special traditions and natural changes.

Every installment features a lovable character who calls that month their favorite, guiding children through a charming, full storybook adventure that captures the spirit of that month (approximately 30 page story). After the story, the fun continues with themed activities perfect for kids to enjoy on their own or with a grown-up—making learning about the months both magical and memorable.

Whether it’s leaf art in September, pumpkin games in October, or snowflake fun in January, Magic Month Club helps children build a joyful connection to the calendar one month at a time through both a complete story with a fun character and also included hands-on activities.

I hope you will enjoy this journey teaching your child what is special about each month of the year.
